CatDescriptText: The women wear name tags that are only slightly legible.  From left to right starting from the second woman from the left, their names might be Mary Lou Butler, Allegheny County, Nonnie S. Miller, Allegheny County and Mary Glaster, Bethesda.
TitMainTitle: Four women in an A & P bakery products booth at a trade show, with sign in background reading "Some of the People Who Help Produce Jane Parker Products" beside portraits of men and women
